    <item>
      <title>行长称通货紧缩将为斯里兰卡人民提供“喘息机会”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/deflation-to-provide-respite-to-sri-lankans-says-governor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡央行行长表示，该国的通货紧缩环境预计将持续到 2025 年初，这凸显了这个南亚国家在前所未有的经济危机中苦苦挣扎于高物价的状况的变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/deflation-to-provide-respite-to-sri-lankans-says-governor</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 08:38:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
